'''Igures''' d yiwet n taddart i d yezgan di tɣiwant n [[At-Yeḥya]] di tanebdaḍt n Tala n Sila deg ugezdu n [[Tizi Wezzu]]

==Aẓar n w'awal==

==Amezruy==
Aɛmer ubuyaḥya d yiwen umrabeḍ si tarwa n sidi buyaḥya , yezdaɣ netta d derya-as tama n wasif ddaw igures , di tgerwla mgal amnekcem afransis (1954) tefka d taddart 32 imeɣraṣen am akli ait tayeb , taseɛdit ait tayeb ,muḥend lɛerbi neɣ buseɛd oudjidane. syina mi yefra ṭrad, ulin atas imezdaɣ d asawen seg wasif mi yuɣen tiferkiwin ɣer taddart n [[at mlal]] id yezgan s ufella n igures .


==Tarakalt==
Taddart Igures tesɛa tilisa nettat d [[At Mlal]], [[Ta_ɣiwant_n_At_Bu_Yusef|At Bu Yusef]] ([[Tifeṛḍud]])  [[Iferḥunen]](ibelqisen).


==Iderman==
Tebḍa taddart ɣef 4 n txelǧatin :
# At Ṭeyeb
# At Weftis
# Igujilen
# At Aɛmer

Degs 5 n yismawen n twacult:
# Ait Tayeb
# Oudjidane
# Ait Mouhoub
# Ait Moufek
# Ben Abderrahmane





